{"tid":2169704,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩諗到條物理題","createTime":"2020-08-22T16:54:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T22:16:34.000Z","uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c298edee97d7ce17436ab2f7aa426e52c0667219","tid":2169704,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T16:54:11.000Z","msg":"我用飲水機&ldquo;針&rdquo;水<br />\n請問水位喺個杯上升既速度係幾多？<br />\n假設水由飲水機出黎既速度係p m^3/s<br />\nV,r,h=volume, radius, height of 個杯 respectively<br />\nBy V=pi*r^2*h,<br />\ndV/dt = pi(r^2*dh/dt) = p<br />\n但我諗到兩個問題：<br />\n1)一開始d水倒落個杯底，d水應該會radially咁向外擴散，咁個radius of the water poured 應該係增加緊？但以上條式冇考慮到呢個因素<br />\n2)如果個杯放得越低，咁d水到達個杯前既速度應該會越高，因為有地心吸力，咁水位向上升既速度都會相應高左？但以上條式都冇考慮到呢個因素<br />\n求解答"},{"pid":"f9eb737122f88db1edcaa6c0cdf69cc7fc3f3f67","tid":2169704,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T16:57:22.000Z","msg":"斟。"},{"pid":"df75009d7e7d732fe82aa6ca3babf2c381c6503a","tid":2169704,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T16:57:39.000Z","msg":"1)岩岩諗到，d水radially咁向外擴散嗰陣，h=0，dh/dt=0，因為d水覆蓋左成個杯面先會向上升<br />\n咁諗岩唔岩"},{"pid":"27d181bf88bbec2ad94d3cd064c0e2cd18045dd2","tid":2169704,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T16:57:55.000Z","msg":"香港人唔好咁撚蠢啦 ｜ FC都唔做就科水  黃圈d錢咁易水架咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2169686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2169686</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e7090bc1872bf4929153d6e3a102dffd577fd4e8","tid":2169704,"uid":302976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T16:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128688913557ff9238d135614183de34ca651971","tid":2169704,"uid":297436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:02:29.000Z","msg":"Model嘅重點就係Approximation<br />\n咁一定會有啲Edge位係唔準確<br />\n但整體夠用就得"},{"pid":"0092d5766ed8330c39594bf4da47ef1fed0c5d25","tid":2169704,"uid":269608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:02:33.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係好明<br />\n<br />\n但你講到一開始radius係個變數<br />\n<br />\n咁起碼條式會有dr/dt?<br />\n要等佢去到填滿晒個底個r先係constant?<br />\n<br />\n利申：廢up"},{"pid":"e8051bc27dd800f5ca825140fa234beab514688f","tid":2169704,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df75009d7e7d732fe82aa6ca3babf2c381c6503a","tid":2169704,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T16:57:39.000Z","msg":"1)岩岩諗到，d水radially咁向外擴散嗰陣，h=0，dh/dt=0，因為d水覆蓋左成個杯面先會向上升<br />\n咁諗岩唔岩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:03:11.000Z","msg":"你係計就計埋反彈/surface tension 之類<br />\n所以其實計唔到, 最接近係要用電腦模擬"},{"pid":"c81753d15dd0311f7f0c1c06b59cb84f752ae816","tid":2169704,"uid":297436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8051bc27dd800f5ca825140fa234beab514688f","tid":2169704,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df75009d7e7d732fe82aa6ca3babf2c381c6503a","tid":2169704,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T16:57:39.000Z","msg":"1)岩岩諗到，d水radially咁向外擴散嗰陣，h=0，dh/dt=0，因為d水覆蓋左成個杯面先會向上升<br />\n咁諗岩唔岩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:03:11.000Z","msg":"你係計就計埋反彈/surface tension 之類<br />\n所以其實計唔到, 最接近係要用電腦模擬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:05:54.000Z","msg":"真係去到咁Detail嘅話<br />\n其實 t tends to 0 嗰下啲水應該係接近Cone咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b41cc6a5ee7df1f4678fa712079120f61dfbe0","tid":2169704,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:06:17.000Z","msg":"1） r^2 都係variable，應該都要用h表達r再d，應該dh/dt 同dV/dt 唔係linear relationship <br />\n<br />\n利申：中學程度數學，有錯勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6fde3f281eb1389fd8a6dc69f41115054ecfa5","tid":2169704,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0092d5766ed8330c39594bf4da47ef1fed0c5d25","tid":2169704,"uid":269608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:02:33.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係好明<br />\n<br />\n但你講到一開始radius係個變數<br />\n<br />\n咁起碼條式會有dr/dt?<br />\n要等佢去到填滿晒個底個r先係constant?<br />\n<br />\n利申：廢up"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:06:38.000Z","msg":"radius r係水杯既半徑，係constant<br />\n至於水radially向外擴散既radius係增加緊<br />\n兩個應該冇關係"},{"pid":"0e324fc1c89af7bfa2d21a719ddd5c6ff9b9259c","tid":2169704,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2aeb17d15febb75e2f1738b5d698ac79a2d79eb1","tid":2169704,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10b41cc6a5ee7df1f4678fa712079120f61dfbe0","tid":2169704,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:06:17.000Z","msg":"1） r^2 都係variable，應該都要用h表達r再d，應該dh/dt 同dV/dt 唔係linear relationship <br />\n<br />\n利申：中學程度數學，有錯勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:08:34.000Z","msg":"Sor，get錯，係圓底杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以為係cone <br />\n自膠"},{"pid":"711f03786b0d3c101b9ebce1f882bd67ceab7267","tid":2169704,"uid":297436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e6fde3f281eb1389fd8a6dc69f41115054ecfa5","tid":2169704,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0092d5766ed8330c39594bf4da47ef1fed0c5d25","tid":2169704,"uid":269608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:02:33.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係好明<br />\n<br />\n但你講到一開始radius係個變數<br />\n<br />\n咁起碼條式會有dr/dt?<br />\n要等佢去到填滿晒個底個r先係constant?<br />\n<br />\n利申：廢up"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:06:38.000Z","msg":"radius r係水杯既半徑，係constant<br />\n至於水radially向外擴散既radius係增加緊<br />\n兩個應該冇關係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:08:40.000Z","msg":"你Integrate嘅時候<br />\nr 其實係水面嘅Radius<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以dr/dt|t=0 唔會係Constant嚟"},{"pid":"9085e9f4a8997208c82947b04e40620a5920127d","tid":2169704,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:08:45.000Z","msg":"2)點解釋？"},{"pid":"0e789534a3a83dbdc8d59fb532c2821fdca0a17e","tid":2169704,"uid":173990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:09:30.000Z","msg":"水位上升因素:<br />\n<br />\n1. rate of water going into the cup<br />\n<br />\n2. cross-sectional area of the cup (assume cylindrical)<br />\n<br />\n所以師兄講嘅radius 同 水落入杯底嘅速度無關。<br />\n<br />\nradius 問題同入嘅速度只係佢落入杯嘅狀態同momentum change 嘅過程，係第二個問題。<br />\n<br />\n可以簡單啲咁睇，<br />\ndV/dt of water = base Area of cup x dh/dt<br />\n<br />\n未必啱㗎，帶返個頭盔先頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678e1e0cfcfe2e3200d622111cf182dd0cf1cf86","tid":2169704,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:09:32.000Z","msg":"其實呢宜家李嘉誠呢就收購亞視黎講呢<br />\n我覺得有得玩架 喂 唔係我呢個李加乘喎<br />\n係穿膠花起朵果個李嘉誠呀<br />\n咁點解 因為佢同中方本身個關係幾好喇<br />\n我諗tvb都要俾番幾分薄面佢架<br />\n同時呢 阿李嘉誠為左收取收視<br />\n我相信佢會搵阿史提芬史匹堡 開一部新一輯既<br />\n&quot;我和疆屍有個約會之未來報告&quot;黎到對撼無綫ge<br />\n而邵逸夫睇到當然唔順眼喇 佢一定會搵阿王晶黎到開一輯<br />\n新既&quot;妙手仁心之流星花園&quot;黎到對撼ge<br />\n到時阿邵逸夫仲會應該係留長返髮黎到擔綱演出<br />\n我諗大家觀眾呢到時一定係大飽眼福ge 你同唔同意呀?"},{"pid":"2760497d74e676e63cb7dc0c335ef1c70955f6ff","tid":2169704,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"711f03786b0d3c101b9ebce1f882bd67ceab7267","tid":2169704,"uid":297436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e6fde3f281eb1389fd8a6dc69f41115054ecfa5","tid":2169704,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0092d5766ed8330c39594bf4da47ef1fed0c5d25","tid":2169704,"uid":269608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:02:33.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係好明<br />\n<br />\n但你講到一開始radius係個變數<br />\n<br />\n咁起碼條式會有dr/dt?<br />\n要等佢去到填滿晒個底個r先係constant?<br />\n<br />\n利申：廢up"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T17:06:38.00